                    <div class="remarks">
                        <p style="margin-bottom: 8px;">
                            Parkside Flats, a 47 unit multifamily property located at 1000 Parr Hill Drive in Martensville, Saskatchewan, sold on May 19, 2023, for $9,310,000 or $198,085 per unit. The property on 10300036 Saskatchewan Ltd. for $9,310,000. Constructed in 2008, Parkside Flats is a wood-frame apartment building that offers modern finishes, in-suite laundry, and access to surface parking.
                        </p>
                        <p>
